:markdown
  ===========================

  There are several different ways in which you can help improve WindUp:

  * It can be as simple as hanging out in the [user forums](https://community.jboss.org/en/windup?view=discussions) and helping other users by answering their questions. 
  * Helping by creating articles related to WindUp usage
  * Add to our documentation through the [GitHub wiki](https://github.com/windup/windup/wiki)
  * Trying out WindUp on your applications and [report any issues](https://community.jboss.org/en/windup?view=discussions)
  * Providing patches or getting involved in the development activities
    * [Fork our code](https://github.com/windup/windup) on GitHub to provide patches
    * Get involved with the development join (windup-dev@lists.jboss.org)[https://lists.jboss.org/mailman/listinfo/windup-dev]
    * (Join)[http://webchat.freenode.net/?channels=#windup] our IRC channel on FreeNode: #windup
  * Any other possible way you can think of. All help is welcome!

